44
00:01:43.030 --> 00:01:45.020
which is the Integrated Development Environment,

45
00:01:45.020 --> 00:01:49.050
the one-stop solution to do all our development activity.

46
00:01:49.050 --> 00:01:53.060
We would be going for the Java Enterprise Eclipse IDE,

47
